@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontColor black
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam PackageBorderColor black
skinparam PackageFontColor black
skinparam ComponentBorderColor black
skinparam ComponentFontColor black
skinparam Shadowing false
title Athena Model Types -> Forms (Before)

package "App Form Layer" {
  component "React Hook Form\nuseForm<T>" as RHF
  component "Zod Schema\nparse/transform" as ZOD
  component "Manual Null/Empty Shim\nper-form mapping code" as SHIM
}

package "Athena SDK" {
  component "defineModel<Row, Insert, Update>" as MODEL
  component "InsertOf / UpdateOf\nType helpers" as TYPES
}

RHF --> SHIM : defaultValues + submit payload
ZOD --> SHIM : input/output transforms
MODEL --> TYPES
TYPES --> SHIM : custom type adaption
SHIM --> MODEL : handcrafted insert/update payload

note right of SHIM
Each form re-implements:
- null <-> empty-string rules
- nullable field handling
- payload cleanup
end note
@enduml
